    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing function over form. The exterior shows some signs of age, including noticeable scratches on the passenger side and minor fading of the clear coat on the roof. Mechanically, it starts consistently and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 20500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly impeccable condition. This specimen has been preserved to exacting showroom standards, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original aesthetic integrity. Meticulously inspected and curated, it represents the absolute pinnacle of its class, offering the discerning enthusiast an uncompromising ownership experience. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this investment-grade motorcar and appreciate its pristine state firsthand.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my pride and joy! This car is honestly a total dream\u2014it's in absolutely stunning shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept it pampered and garage-stored, so the paint is flawless and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like a cloud and has been loved every single mile. I'm really looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. The S54B32 power plant remains in peak factory specification, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. This unit features a documented subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled cooling system with an aluminum radiator. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a variable M-differential lock that remains tight. The exterior retains its factory-correct depth and luster, free of rock chips or paint correction artifacts. Underneath, the bushings are pliable and the suspension geometry is dialed to factory alignment specs. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Zero mechanical issues. Clean title in hand. No accidents.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a multi-layer ceramic coating. All body panels are perfectly aligned with factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since new. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule at authorized service centers, with a complete binder of service records included in the sale. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, showing no leaks or aging hoses. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a 'time capsule' vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been curated with exacting standards. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that remains devoid of wear or imperfection. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new unit, offering a driving experience that satisfies the most rigorous inspections. This is a definitive opportunity to acquire a specimen of remarkable preservation and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    }
